The Glenn Beck Program - 09/05/13 









The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET,


Doc Thompson fills in for Glenn Beck.

 Doc brings up how Obama is trying to manipulate the numbers and cook the books
 with both the national debt and federal worker raises.

 Also, what is Obama trying to hide by drawing our attention to Syria?
 Benghazi?
 Obama care?
 The debt ceiling?
 Doc outlines the many reasons why we shouldn't trust this administration.
